meyhaneyi işleten...

1094
01:15:31,535 --> 01:15:34,322
...John Lloyd'la görüştünüz mü?

1095
01:15:34,330 --> 01:15:35,866
Evet, suikasttan hemen sonra.

1096
01:15:35,873 --> 01:15:40,242
Size Bayan Surratt'ın...

1097
01:15:40,252 --> 01:15:41,752
